Title: Fix "invalid byte in UTF-8 sequence" error in EC
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Component: ec
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
State: unknown
Version: 1.6.0p23
Date: 1617874169

An error in the agent protocol could, in some cases, send an
invalid payload to the core.  The core would then spam the event
console with "invalid byte XXX in UTF-8 sequence" messages
making the event console unusable.
